00:44:24,210 --> 00:44:25,569
Madame Xu,

747
00:44:26,049 --> 00:44:27,730
you've read these few lines many times.

748
00:44:27,810 --> 00:44:29,129
What are your thoughts exactly?

749
00:44:29,609 --> 00:44:30,650
Sanniang's life is at stake.

750
00:44:30,810 --> 00:44:32,370
She is waiting for us to rescue her.

751
00:44:32,810 --> 00:44:34,049
We must save her.

752
00:44:35,250 --> 00:44:36,330
But we can't confront

753
00:44:36,409 --> 00:44:38,170
the 300,000 soldiers directly
no matter what.

754
