00:44:45,810 --> 00:44:49,250
For such a low-level position,

758
00:44:50,609 --> 00:44:52,409
why does he have to go to such lengths

759
00:44:52,409 --> 00:44:53,969
to get it?

760
00:44:57,409 --> 00:45:00,810
Right, what gains have you made
from this trip to the capital?

761
00:45:04,770 --> 00:45:05,810
I followed him all along

762
00:45:06,129 --> 00:45:07,290
to the Dali Court.

763
00:45:07,609 --> 00:45:09,810
He met Vice President Wang.

764
00:45:10,529 --> 00:45:12,850
As for the rest, I have no clue.

765
00:45:13,049 --> 00:45:14,089
Right, I've asked around.

766
00:45:14,290 --> 00:45:17,409
Vice President Wang is in charge
of the Right Court.

767
00:45:22,170 --> 00:45:24,730
The Right Court.

768
00:45:26,650 --> 00:45:29,250
The director of Embroidery Office.

769
00:45:34,650 --> 00:45:37,770
What a cunning plan.

770
00:45:39,049 --> 00:45:41,449
What tricks
is Wu Lian playing this time?

771
